<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<appendix xml:id="app-f-table">
  <title>The F Distribution</title>

  <p>This appendix gives right-tail critical values for the <term>F distribution<idx><h>appendices</h><h>F table</h></idx></term>. Each entry <m>F_\alpha(d_1,d_2)</m> satisfies <m>P(F&gt;F_\alpha)=\alpha</m>, where <m>d_1</m> is the numerator degrees of freedom and <m>d_2</m> is the denominator degrees of freedom.</p>
  <p>Because the full <m>F</m> table is large, the values are split into smaller tables by significance level and numerator degrees of freedom.</p>

